  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_000&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今日も昨日も、
夕飯にメザシが出るんじゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She did it yesterday and again
today... Why is she so evil...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わしは魚がキライなのに、
うちの嫁は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She knows I hate fish, but that's
all we have back home...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273760</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>彼ったら、うちで
ゴロゴロ、ゴロゴロ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's such a drama queen.
Always yelling and yelling...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273760</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私が仕事に行くって言ったら、
俺と仕事どっちが大事だ！
って……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>"I'm going to work", I tell him, but
"Your job is crap compared to mine!"
is all he says... Jerk...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273928</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ママが、ぼくの
海賊チョコカードを
全部、捨てたんだぁ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mommy ate all of my pirate
Choco-Cards! All of them!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273928</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、海賊チョコカード
ってのは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My beloved pirate Choco-Cards...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぶっちゃけ暇なのよ。
仕事ないかなぁ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's got so much time, he said.
He doesn't have a job.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、力仕事はイヤ。
頭使うのもムリ。
人と話すのも苦手で……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If the job is too hard, it's rough.
If it's too boring it's silly. If there
are too many people, it's bad... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>グチグチグチグチ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Blah blah blah blah blah...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274232</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_130_050_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ～ん、&lt;Mint&gt;さん！
早く戻ってきて～！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aaah! Miss &lt;Mint&gt;! Please come back
soon! I can't take this anymore! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
